        </p>
        <p>Yours Sincerely,</p>
        <h4 style="font-weight: 600; padding-bottom: -.5rem; margin: 0">Patrick
          Kenneford Annan,</h4>
        <p style="font-weight: 600; padding-bottom: -.5rem; margin: 0">Head of
